description.en-us: Pull-Back Speeders are a line of 1:43 scale pull-back cars with moving parts, featuring a mix of licensed and fantasy castings. Not to be confused with the unrelated 1:43 Pull-Backs . Notably all cars are marked as made in Thailand or China.
